HEADWORD: Epileptic
<hw>Ep`i*lep"tic</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One affected with
epilepsy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A medicine for the cure of epilepsy.</def>⟦br⟧
